Lectura y selecci√≥n de la base de datos

ICFES201502 <- read.csv2("20152.csv", skip = 5)
ICFES201502_1 <- droplevels(subset(ICFES201502, (JORNADA %in% 
                          c("COMPLETA U ORDINARIA","MA√ëANA","TARDE")) &
                          CALENDARIO == "A"))
cp1 <- princomp(subset(ICFES201502_1, 
               select = PROMLECTURACRITICA:PROMCOMPETENCIASCIUDADAN),
               cor = FALSE)
summary(cp1)

Desplieque de los componentes principales

factor_exp <- 60
with(cp1, plot(scores[,1], scores[,2], 
               asp = 1, pch = 19, col = "gray30",
               xlab = "Componente principal 1",
               ylab = "Componente principal 2"))
abline(h = 0, col = "blue")
abline(v = 0, col = "blue")
segments(0, 0, cp1$loadings[,1]*factor_exp,
         cp1$loadings[,2]*factor_exp, col = "red")
text(cp1$loadings[,1]*factor_exp, cp1$loadings[,2]*factor_exp,
    substring(names(cp1$center),5), pos = 2, col = "red", cex = 0.7)

Visualizaci√≥n conjunta de CP y Cluster

colores <- c("turquoise","darkgreen","red","brown","magenta")
with(cp1, plot(scores[,1], scores[,2], 
               asp = 1, pch = 19,
               xlab = "Componente principal 1",
               ylab = "Componente principal 2",
     col = colores[ICFES201502_1$grupo]))
abline(h = 0, col = "black")
abline(v = 0, col = "black")
legend("topright", legend = paste("grupo",1:5),
       col = colores, pch = 19)
